270	/**
271	 * Org-Scoped Procedure
272	 *
273	 * For org-level operations: repositories, members, integrations.
274	 * Only accepts clerk-active users (authenticated + has claimed org).
275	 *
276	 * Type-safe: `ctx.auth.orgId` is guaranteed to exist.
277	 *
278	 * Use cases:
